<plot>Granas was the god of light. Valmar was the god of darkness. Eons ago, an epic battle between the two - known as 'The Battle of Good and Evil' - ruined the paradise that was once the world of Grandia II. The resulting end of that battle resulted in Valmar's destruction, Granas going into a deep sleep, and a scar around the world left by Granas' sword. But now Valmar is about to be revived. And what of Granas? Will his followers be able to wake him before Valmar revives? Play along as Ryudo, his pal [and pet bird] Skye, and the friends and enemies they meet, go on the epic journey to stop Valmar's return.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?221739</url></doc>
